node.text: LIVE NOW! The @randygmoss Straight Bass Classic video at the link in our bio. We helped put on this amazing event for an even better cause. Go check out how the tourney played out and donate to DYRK1A if you can, an organization helping those affected by a rare genetic disorder affecting one of Moss' closest friends. That’s @lipripper863 on the squad with him
